bs and bosses. </li></ul><br><img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/367080/extras/SteamScene6.png?t=1506401946\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Secrets of the Cacti</h2><br>Everywhere one looks, there is much that is not seen. Concealed treasures abound. By eating cacti, Roq gains psychedelic powers and is able to perceive the secrets that lurk in plain sight.<br><br>Some items Roq discovers can be combined to create distinct artifacts. Find a blink orb and a fire cube? Take these to the droidsmith aboard Songbringer to craft a fire orb enabling Roq to teleport forward a few steps while turning into a fireball.<br><br>Songbringer features no experience points (no XP). Progress is made by crushing mobs, vanquishing bosses and claiming lost technological devices.<br><br><img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/367080/extras/SteamScene4.png?t=1506401946\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Leaderboard</h2><br>On completing a quest, several factors are quantified to produce an overall score:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Time to complete<br></li><li>Percentage of map uncovered<br></li><li>Percentage of items obtained<br></li><li>Game mode: regular vs permadeath</li></ul><br>Your score can be saved to a global leaderboard sorted by world seed. This leaderboard cycles through seeds by popularity and freshness. You can manually override to view a particular seed.<br><br><img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/367080/extras/SteamScene5.png?t=1506401946\">", "developers": ["Wizard Fu Games"], "support_info": {"url": "http://steamcommunity.com/app/367080/discussions/", "email": ""}, "publishers": ["Wizard Fu Games"], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "1 Sep, 2017"}, "detailed_description": "<h1>Buzz</h1><p><img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/367080/extras/SteamQuotes.png?t=1506401946\"></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/367080/extras/SteamScene1.png?t=1506401946\"><br